Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了  好紧张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正宋黑_GBK\bord0\fs40\pos(1023,458)\c&H3B5E78&}京都府吹奏乐竞赛会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs40\fsp5\pos(1070,715)\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fscx95\c&H55809F&}关西吹奏乐竞赛会京都府预赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我去和麻美报告一下  她太紧张躲进洗手间里了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这次将出席关西大赛的学校是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,金奖…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说是废金但到底是金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,高坂同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,高兴得泣不成声了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了呢  拿到了金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,痛不欲生般的不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么大家会为了一块废金而高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的目标难道不是全国大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的觉得我们能参加全国大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你就没有不甘心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,「进入高中胸部就会变大」这种传言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么会去相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怀揣着对今后的各种期待  我的高中生活拉开了序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,特意选择这所不怎么会遇到初中同学的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为自己所憧憬的水手服只有这里有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,和想重新开始新的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,各位新入学的同学们  欢迎来到北宇治高中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是吹奏部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们祝贺青春闪耀的各位入学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这完全不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,太烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不整齐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,音调不合  节奏也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看上去也不像是以全国为目标的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那个真的很烂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才你不是说了很烂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,说出声了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来  你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我{\rsymbol}?{\r}  我叫加藤叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,座位在你后面  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫黄前久美子  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  到底是什么烂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,都高中生了还在教室里大吵大闹的可不是什么光彩的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这裙子长度怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快调整好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是担任这1年3班班主任的  松本美知惠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,首先先点个名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,麻井雄大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,石川有希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,内山田宏子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,江口洋子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,黄前久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,加藤叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,川岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,绿…辉{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3\pos(1045,990)}蓝宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那个读「Sapphire」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,写作「绿辉」读作「Sapphire」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3\pos(1055,990)}Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,川岛…绿辉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sapphire吗  好帅气
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}不好意思  下次不会读错了\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子  一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,名字没叫错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我叶月就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,或者加藤也行  按你喜欢的叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没有和你一起回去的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我呢  决定要在高中交新的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,做许多从未尝试过的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以请多多指教  久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准雅宋_GBK\fs70\pos(1090,700)\3c&H935004&}{\bord1.5\blur2\fad(500,0)}欢迎来到高中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,话说  你之前说什么东西烂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那个就别提了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3\pos(982,990)}蛋白石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  Opal酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,错了  是那种更偏向绿色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那个那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是大号君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大号君好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我好喜欢它  能让我摸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,呐  Opal酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3\pos(990,990)}Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫绿辉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  Sapphire酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  好可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大号的吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,大号{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,铜管乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,铜管乐器{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小绿我曾经是吹奏部的  乐器是低音大提琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,低音大提琴{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小绿{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小绿就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3\pos(610,990)}Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,「绿辉」这叫法总感觉有点那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果以后能称呼我为小绿的话就太感谢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,然后  低音大提琴是乐器的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这么大的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,像大怪物版的小提琴一样的东西  知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那个我看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看到过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前也是吹奏部的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗  那个你叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,黄前久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,叫久美子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫叶月  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I copy{\rsymbol}!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子是哪个分组的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,低音…乐器是悠风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此  和你的风格很像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,诶  UFO{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不是UFO  是悠风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3\pos(1022,990)}Euphonium
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,全称叫悠风号…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  类似小尺寸的这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,诶  相当小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我呢  到初中为止一直是网球部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,到了高中想试试吹奏乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗  小绿现在正好要去吹奏部参观
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意的话  大家一起去怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord0\c&H3B403D&\pos(899,870)}欢迎来到吹奏部  向音乐教室前进吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害  那个是小号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得那个很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快看快看  叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那个就是悠风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  UFO好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪久美子说比大号君要小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,萨克斯也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,叶月…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们难道是过来参观的吗  快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on  Join us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哇塞  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来来  这就是我校的吹奏部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是第一批来参观的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以作为纪念送你们颗糖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说好了新生大多很紧张  不要随便上去搭话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那么快就把她们吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  你们慢慢看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,铜奖…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,呐  久美子  那个四方形的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是校音器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,用那个来校正音的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧  难道你是新手{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊  那我就从吹奏乐的基础开始教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,明  日  香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,降B调
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,长号  好好对准
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,圆号  音偏了  好好听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,用校音器好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,音不是很整齐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,高坂同学{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是来参观的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我想入部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到吹奏部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,梨子  快点拿入部申请来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了  她要是逃了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会  她又不是小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多该走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那个女生  真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,与其说是熟人  只是初中曾一起在吹奏部而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就是熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  这所高中的吹奏部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,比想象的更…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,更不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,诶  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他们在府大赛的目标只是银奖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,得到银奖的话不是很厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.5\an1\c&HCBD3C5&\fs50\frz22.358\move(538,165,347,165,0,5905)}乐谱\N\h还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正北魏楷书_GBK\bord0\c&H302C2C&\an8\move(233,659,42,659,0,5905)}目标\N全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果想去关西大赛或者全国大赛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,必须在各大赛中获得金奖才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而且即使获得金奖  废金也是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,废…废金是什么
Comment: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,（吹奏乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H53473F&\fs40\an7\bord1\shad1\4c&H755B89&\move(1186,743,938,743,0,5402)\3c&H755B89&}初学者·有经验者…\N无论是谁都Welcome
Comment: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1107,959)}特别是男生）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,吹奏乐竞赛会分为金  银  铜三个奖项
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,代表是从金奖获得者中挑选的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,获得金奖却没被选中就是废金了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就像Sapphire酱说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,想要进军接下来的大赛  废金是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,太难懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们三个要是入部的话  不是能成为救世主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没那么简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小绿会加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我最喜欢音乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我坚信无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,音乐都是人们将真情传递出去的强有力语言之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,红绿灯一直都没有变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  小绿忘记按按钮了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了  Sapphire酱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,叫人家小绿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,关于吹奏部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,再考虑考虑吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,电车来了  我往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的烂  是指吹奏部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,高坂同学竟然会在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她那么棒  我还以为会去洛秋或者立华高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,大意什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,秀一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  对青梅竹马也不打个招呼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,明明还是同一所学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,头发束起来了{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,话说  高坂丽奈也在这所学校  完全不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来…你的反应是不是略慢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫我别和你说话的  我只是遵照你说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,诶{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,初三的时候  你不是说过「不要和我说话  丑女」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那还不是因为你在大家面前问我「今天要在我家吃饭吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不对  现在不是呆在这的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  你社团打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还没决定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不加入吹奏部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我没什么其他想做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,应该会加吹奏部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不加入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然想过加入  但还是决定放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没为什么  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,高中怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一般般…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来帮忙准备晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,吹奏部…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的觉得我们能参加全国大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有恶意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只是将想到的事脱口而出了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也觉得能拿到金奖是很不错的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是废金也是了不起的金奖…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还扎了个小马尾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,高中第一天就干劲足过头了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,话说  别随便开我的房门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是是  抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了别随便开我的房门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你要放弃吹奏乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么{\rsymbol}?{\r}  因为那是北宇治
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看  让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,「末吉」和「吉」哪个好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不是「末吉」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,从上开始是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,「大吉」「中吉」「小吉」「吉」「半吉」「末吉」「末小吉」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说「吉」比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是久违地想来抽一支签试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是「运动会」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是「天国与地狱」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,准确的说是「地狱中的奥菲欧」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是首非常棒的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,早饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,吹不出声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,诶  那个号嘴是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯{\rsymbol}?{\r}  我买的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,买的{\rsymbol}?{\r}  你已经买好了{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  就买了这个号嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你太性急了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,明明乐器都还没决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样才能吹响它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,小绿是拉低音大提琴的不太懂  教教我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴唇…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要让嘴唇像这样震动起来  卟的一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,做做看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然后  这样对着号嘴试试
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,出声了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才出声了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,出声了  吹出声音来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对了对了  久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不一起加入吹奏部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样  我加入了北宇治高中吹奏乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.26,0:22:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,然后  下一首乐曲开始了
Comment: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:45.61,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,==============OP JP=================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:45.61,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}叶えたいことが溢れてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:51.19,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}立ち止まってる暇なんてないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:57.86,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸に秘めたあこがれをフルボリュームで届けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:02.54,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}行こう…  クレッシェンドの向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:05.81,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}つまずいてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:08.64,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}はみだしてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:17.21,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君の音色を僕たちは待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:25.85,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響け！  生まれたての夢つめ込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:31.83,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大きな空へいま旅立とう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:37.42,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}拓け！  笑顔を味方につけて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:43.31,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}離さない  諦めたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:48.42,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}限界さえも跳ね返す勇気で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:52.71,oped_ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}DREAM  SOLISTER
Comment: 1,0:03:41.15,0:03:45.61,oped_zh,,0,0,0,,==============OP CN=================
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.15,0:03:45.61,oped_zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要实现的梦想不断涌现
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.90,0:03:51.19,oped_zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没有余暇在此止步不前
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.72,0:03:57.86,oped_zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将内心潜藏的憧憬用最大乐声传递出去
